# ╔══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╗
# ║  .gitignore — Cloud Computing Security                   ║
# ║  Ne JAMAIS exposer de secrets sur GitHub                 ║
# ╚══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╝

# === CLÉS ET CREDENTIALS AWS ===
*.pem
*.key
*.ppk
credentials
.aws/
*access_key*
*secret_key*

# === VARIABLES D'ENVIRONNEMENT ===
.env
.env.*
*.secret
*password*

# === SYSTÈME D'EXPLOITATION ===
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
Desktop.ini
*~

# === ÉDITEURS ===
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo

# === LOGS ET TEMPORAIRES ===
*.log
*.tmp
*.temp

# === FICHIERS VOLUMINEUX ===
*.iso
*.tar.gz
*.zip
